# SpoolSense Scanner Libraries

Tag format parsers and NFC protocol libraries. Each library is standalone
C/C++ with no Arduino dependencies, making them testable natively.

## Libraries

### openprinttag/
OpenPrintTag encoder/decoder. CBOR-based filament data format over ISO15693 (SLIX2).
Includes a minimal CBOR implementation and NDEF helpers.

### opentag3d/
OpenTag3D encoder/decoder. Fixed binary offset format over ISO14443A (NTAG213/215/216).
Wrapped in NDEF with MIME type `application/opentag3d`. Supports core (102 bytes)
and extended (187 bytes) field sets. v1.000 spec.

### tigertag/
TigerTag parser. Binary format over ISO14443A (NTAG213/215). Includes material,
brand, and aspect lookup tables from the TigerTag public database.

### PN5180/
PN5180 NFC reader driver. SPI register control, ISO15693 and ISO14443A protocol
implementations. Based on the PN5180 Arduino library with ISO14443A extensions.
